{"tid":1002713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★優質150?】社區組織協會幹事：大部分新移民屬「少壯生力軍」怎能令公立醫院淪陷","createTime":"2019-01-31T06:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T13:31:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0998e6737748201b74e1d2120d8e4b18afbe2a82","tid":1002713,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2388725/org/e65b4b50cabaac9123392368157be297.jpg/ViPZFZ6vURaA1npSx7sF1Tv3j243pKWxAE93UABPd1A?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2388725%2Forg%2Fe65b4b50cabaac9123392368157be297.jpg%2FViPZFZ6vURaA1npSx7sF1Tv3j243pKWxAE93UABPd1A%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=31f21bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公營醫療服務緊張，公立醫院醫生人手不足，杏林覺醒成員黃任匡醫生提出應檢討每天150個單程證配額，提出新移民是令本港醫療系統崩潰之因。<br />\n<br />\n關注病人權益的香港<span style=\"color: red;\">社區組織協會幹事彭鴻昌</span>今天（31日）在《明報》撰文，隔空反駁上述說法，指出內地新移民定居本港的人數實際遠低於每年5.4萬的推算，而且大部分年齡均屬「少壯生力軍」，對本港醫療服務需求較少，質疑「又怎能令公立醫院淪陷﹖」<br />\n<br />\n彭鴻昌回覆《香港01》查詢時補充，醫院管理局應更積極招聘合資格的海外醫生，醫務委員會可考慮取消有限度註冊醫生一旦考執業試的實習要求，長遠更應考慮仿效新加坡，設立一份認可的院校名單，讓合資格的醫科畢業生直接申請來港作有限度註冊。<br />\n<br />\n而醫學會副會長林哲玄亦在《明報》撰文，指即使全面仿效新加坡模式，海外醫生在捱過了監督期、取得全面執照後仍會離開公院，斥仿效之法屬「東施效顰」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/290023/%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%BD%AD%E9%B4%BB%E6%98%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%BB%E5%8C%A1%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8E%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E8%AB%96-%E4%BF%83%E4%BB%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F290023%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E6%2598%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25A7%2581%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258C%25A1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%25A8%258E%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E4%25BB%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2581%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B3%2595&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6kUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=fd907c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/290023/%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-%E5%BD%AD%E9%B4%BB%E6%98%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%BB%E5%8C%A1%E6%AA%A2%E8%A8%8E%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E8%AB%96-%E4%BF%83%E4%BB%BF%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95</a>"},{"pid":"cef9ffb65df8fc742b6ad324b572130715ab39ae","tid":1002713,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3789829d9574575addf9ccec80bb05172019b9f2","tid":1002713,"uid":4783,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"中位數年齡4字頭<br />\n點樣少壯生力軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f888d2a164f9b23de70ef9a2e5edb65f59c87329","tid":1002713,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"3789829d9574575addf9ccec80bb05172019b9f2","tid":1002713,"uid":4783,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:54:37.000Z","msg":"中位數年齡4字頭<br />\n點樣少壯生力軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSQAOdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSQAOdh.jpg&h=7e1069fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5b9cc34e7e8eb41d3b2bb35226074c00fa0f678","tid":1002713,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"9up唔洗證據？拎就業數字出黎睇過先啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"3a678497ea0040f522fe67a90e33a966749fb4e4","tid":1002713,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:56:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">華為興衰在此一舉 任正非：過了34歲就是廢人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為公司被爆出辭退34歲以上程式員的消息，這些程式員都已經為公司工作了十多年。展程CEO陳羽翔被指獨吞股權，逼走一起創業七年的程式員伙伴，從時間上來算創業七年也恰巧是30多歲的年紀。任正非解釋道：30多歲的程式員不能熬夜，失去激情30多歲的程式員成本太高，性價比太低，30多歲的程式員在法律上有更多權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.haixiaba.com/n369413.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.haixiaba.com%2Fn369413.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6kUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=17253a05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.haixiaba.com/n369413.html</a>"},{"pid":"7ef087dd70cf8b20e8c7d0b0093554b8686029c0","tid":1002713,"uid":19725,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0998e6737748201b74e1d2120d8e4b18afbe2a82","tid":1002713,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2388725/org/e65b4b50cabaac9123392368157be297.jpg/ViPZFZ6vURaA1npSx7sF1Tv3j243pKWxAE93UABPd1A?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2388725%2Forg%2Fe65b4b50cabaac9123392368157be297.jpg%2FViPZFZ6vURaA1npSx7sF1Tv3j243pKWxAE93UABPd1A%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=31f21bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公營醫療服務緊張，公立醫院醫生人手不足，杏林覺醒成員黃任匡醫生提出應檢討每天150個單程證配額，提出新移民是令本港醫療系統崩潰之因。<br />\n<br />\n關注病人權益的香港<span style=\"color: red;\">社區組織協會幹事彭鴻昌</span>今天（31日）在《明報》撰文，隔空反駁上述說法，指出內地新移民定居本港的人數實際遠低於每年5.4萬的推算，而且大部分年齡均屬「少壯生力軍」，對本港醫療服務需求較少，質疑「又怎能令公立醫院淪陷﹖」<br />\n<br />\n彭鴻昌回覆《香港01》查詢時補充，醫院管理局應更積極招聘合資格的海外醫生，醫務委員會可考慮取消有限度註冊醫生一旦考執業試的實習要求，長遠更應考慮仿效新加坡，設立一